### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/pymmdrza/envfy.git
cd envfy

# Create development environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .[dev]

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
black envfy/
isort envfy/

# Lint code
flake8 envfy/
mypy envfy/
```

